title: Move In Specials for Immediate Move Ins! Call and Tour Today!
posting_body: ['Olympic Village Apartments, located in Bremerton.', 'Minutes away from bus routes, naval shipyard, and shopping mall.', 'Olympic Village features luxurious resort style amenities, making your home feel like a vacation.', 'Enjoy updated styles and modern apartment homes in the ideal location.', 'With 1,2, and 3-bedroom floor plans we have the perfect home for anyone!', 'We even want you to bring your furry friends (ask us about our pet policy).', 'Our beautiful property has so much to offer, from spacious floor plans to gourmet style kitchens.', 'Enjoy the convenience of in-home washer and dryer and wood burning fireplace in every unit.', 'Our amenities include:', '• Indoor Pool and Spa', '• Outdoor Pool', '• Fitness Center', '• Business Center', '• Basketball Gym', '• Racquetball Court', '• Renovated Clubhouse with kitchen', '• Playground', 'Call Olympic Village your home today!', 'Contact our leasing office for more information and to schedule a tour.', 'Or apply here: <URL>/', 'Leasing Office open 7 days a week for your convenience.', 'Mon-Fri 9:00-6:00', 'Sat-Sun 10:00-5:00', '1381 NE Fairgrounds Road, Bremerton, WA 98311']
